name: places/ChIJPbeCWGMZ2jERFKUCshDWGo0/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUMyanNySlR3EAE
text:
{'text': 'Chanced upon this club while at Albert court Village Hotel, they are located just steps away!

Super cool and chill atmosphere and love the choice of music too.

They have a wide unique range of finger food which is unlike the usual ones they have at other pubs or clubs.

Also wanted to try their karaoke room but it was booked when we came :(

Will definitely be back again!!', 'languageCode': 'en'}

name: places/ChIJPbeCWGMZ2jERFKUCshDWGo0/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNvNVlmVmh3RRAB
text: {'text': "Compared to last Friday, yesterday being the Grand Opening, one would think and expect would have been much better, the place was Packed, very good, everyone was geared up to enjoy themselves BUT the Whole thing was a Flop as far as I'm concerned, the Sound System was Disastrous, Muffled, Sound balance was totally Out or Not done, weather there was any Sound check done, to me, I lost it  (the mood ) thank Goodness, none of my Family or Friends turned up. Something has to be done, I saw it in the Musicians Face, how disappointed they were and a total let down to their Family, Friends and Music Followers. The Management Must sit down and analyse what went wrong yesterday, if they want the crowd to comeback again or else, we'll just have to take a look at Other Outlets.\nI must Apologise for giving such a Glamorous write up last week and face this sort of Quality Sound, this week. There were other Musicians waiting In and Out of the Pub, eager to play but with this sort of sound, I wouldn't even dare compare it with any of the Hungry Ghost Functions, the Sound System was Fantastic. Let's see what happens next week???????? Jeers.....oops sorry I mean Cheers.", 'languageCode': 'en'}
